title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - Shreddy Krueger
description:
The new Shreddy Krueger is our first System Rocker design built on a performance gun shape. Don’t let this first ever set-back version of the Arbor System catch you off guard - it delivers a deadly level of versatility: bottomless powder, varied speed and terrain, steeps, trees, backcountry freestyle and more - kills it all...
To learn more about the Shreddy Krueger visit: arborcollective.com/snowboards/products/shreddy-krueger/
